WEBVTT

1
01:29:04.290 --> 01:29:06.280 
听说你要走了
I heard you were leaving.

2
01:29:08.100 --> 01:29:11.120 
大村让你取代我，你却要落跑
Omura offers you my job, and you run away.

3
01:29:12.200 --> 01:29:14.400 
我猜我应该谢你
I suppose I should thank you.

4
01:29:14.970 --> 01:29:19.500 
月薪五百元，包括你当俘虏
$500 a month, including back pay for time spent...

5
01:29:19.940 --> 01:29:21.770 
被关起来的慰问金
...in captivity.

6
01:29:23.350 --> 01:29:26.680 
够你下半辈子都泡在酒瓶里
Enough to climb back inside a bottle for the rest of your life.

7
01:29:30.120 --> 01:29:31.550 
不客气
You're welcome.

